name: James Webber
body:
### Hi, I'm James
I'm a graduate student in the [bioinformatics program](http://bioinformatics.ucsf.edu) at [UCSF](http://www.ucsf.edu). I'm a joint student in the [Bandyopadhyay](http://www.cancersignaling.net) and [Krogan](http://kroganlab.ucsf.edu) labs.

### I don't know what I'm doing with this
I'm just procrastinating right now. Maybe I'll put something here later.

### Oh, also
* At one point I was trying to decide on a pair of glasses and I made [Frameshift](http://frameshift.herokuapps.com), a voting website. It is pretty silly. The code isn't on Github yet, I should get on that.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
